<%@ Page Title="Aspire Mail User | Communications Technologies, Inc." Language="C#" MasterPageFile="~/masterpage.master" %>


<asp:Content ID="content" ContentPlaceHolderID="cphMain" runat="Server">
    <h1>Aspire Mail User</h1>
    <h3>To access your mailbox:</h3>
    <ol>
        <li>From your desk:
            <br />
            Lift handset (optional)<br />
            Press V Mail</li>
        <li>From other system phones:
            <br />
            Lift handset or press SPK (speaker phone)<br />
            Dial 600<br />
            Dial your mailbox number when requested</li>
        <li>From outside building:<br />
            Dial phone number<br />
            When auto attendant answers dial #<br />
            DIal your mailbox number</li>
    </ol>
    <h3>To record your greeting:</h3>
    <p>
        Access your mailbox (1, 2 or 3 above)<br />
        Dial 4 (greeting)<br />
        Follow prompts
    </p>
    <h3>To record mailbox name:</h3>
    <p>Access your mailbox (1, 2 or 3 above) dial 76 (record name) follow prompts</p>
    <h3>To program a security code:</h3>
    <p>
        Access your mailbox (1,2 or 3 above)<br />
        Dial 67 (mailbox options)<br />
        Dial 7 (security)<br />
        Follow prompts
    </p>
    <h3>To program notification:</h3>
    <p>
        Access your mailbox (1, 2 or 3 above)<br />
        Dial 67 (mailbox options)<br />
        Dial 6 (notifications)<br />
        Dial 2 (activate) to select notification mode to activate or<br />
        Dial 6 (modify) to program or modify an active mode<br />
        Follow prompts<br />
        Note: for digital pagers, it is necessary to program a dialing pause at the end of the pager telephone number.
    </p>
    <h3>To leave a message for a co-worker:</h3>
    <p>
        Lift handset<br />
        Dial co-workers extension number<br />
        Press vmail or dial 8<br />
    </p>
    <h3>To transfer a caller to a particular mailbox:</h3>
    <p>
        Press hold<br />
        Press vmail or dial 600<br />
        Dial mailbox/extension number<br />
        Hang up. 
    </p>
    <h3>To transfer a caller to the main voicemail greeting</h3>
    <p>
        For retrieving messages<br />
        Press hold<br />
        Dial 600<br />
        Hang up
    </p>
</asp:Content>
